column4: NSLOCTEXT("[8F1B297F418FA5BF9E99EF9C83B830DF]", "DB8FA537454E22598970B18A1BE8AA57", "Oh, I\'m sorry. I forgot to explain.")
NSLOCTEXT("[8F1B297F418FA5BF9E99EF9C83B830DF]", "1A5F06294BFF436E4647DA925CDD912A", "This is a Meat Farm. We grow Meat for everyone.")
NSLOCTEXT("[8F1B297F418FA5BF9E99EF9C83B830DF]", "6D543D1C49529759D25B67A1E34C64DA", "Jiji and I decided to give you three pieces of Meat a day, {Player}")
NSLOCTEXT("[8F1B297F418FA5BF9E99EF9C83B830DF]", "35580C2B411F60B66D1BB5810839DAB4", "What? I gave you Meat today, remember?")
NSLOCTEXT("[8F1B297F418FA5BF9E99EF9C83B830DF]", "6DCFF3F24FBC039B05C279AFDFD6BF67", "If you run out of food, look for mushrooms in Native Forest.")
